title: BIP 52: #wenCLAWS Token Design Contest
body:
TLDR; Select the winning design for the new $CLAWS token.

Prize structure:
- 1st Prize: $500 in $BADGER tokens and 50 [UMA uTVL KPI Options]
- 3 Runners Up: $150 in $BADGER tokens and 15 [UMA uTVL KPI Options]

Link to Discussions and Submissions: https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-52-wenclaws-token-design-contest/4419
